com.complexible.common.openrdf.model

Interface IOGraph

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Collection<org.openrdf.model.Statement>, org.openrdf.model.Graph, Iterable<org.openrdf.model.Statement>, Serializable
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ExtGraph

    public interface IOGraph
extends org.openrdf.model.Graph

    Extends the standard Sesame Graph to provide some RDF IO methods for inserting data from input or writing the Graph out.

    Since:
    0.8
    See Also:
    GraphIO
